% The code assumes that the Path folder contains one folder per subject
% with an anatomical image and raw multiparametric images in subfolders or
% by themselves.
% Ex: Path --> Subject 1 --> T1
%                            FLAIR
%                            pCASL
%                            PERF
%                            Relax
